                  <div id="innerbodycontent" class="row nolayout"><div class="offset1 span10">
            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Using "ba" sentences</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="ibox" class="toc">
	<div class="ibox-link"><span class="plainlinks"><a href="ASG2UB2B" class="mw-redirect" title="ASG2UB2B"><img src="https&#58;//resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/silk/link.png" /></a></span></div>
	<ul class="ibox-list">
               <li class="ibox-level-cefr-hsk clearfix">
                        
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><span style="font-size: 1.4em;"><a href="B1_grammar_points" title="B1 grammar points"> B1</a></span> / <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><a href="HSK3_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK3 grammar points">HSK3</a></span></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level clearfix" style="display:none">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="B1_grammar_points" title="B1 grammar points"> B1</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="HSK3_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK3 grammar points"> HSK3</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Advanced_uses_of_&quot;ba&quot;" title="Advanced uses of &quot;ba&quot;">Advanced uses of "ba"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Using_&quot;jiang&quot;_as_a_formal_&quot;ba&quot;" title="Using &quot;jiang&quot; as a formal &quot;ba&quot;">Using "jiang" as a formal "ba"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B2</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Advanced_uses_of_&quot;ba&quot;" title="Advanced uses of &quot;ba&quot;">Advanced uses of "ba"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK5</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Using_&quot;jiang&quot;_as_a_formal_&quot;ba&quot;" title="Using &quot;jiang&quot; as a formal &quot;ba&quot;">Using "jiang" as a formal "ba"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK5</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-usedfor clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Used for</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Expressing_passive_voice" title="Expressing passive voice">Expressing passive voice</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="把" title="把">把</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/2e/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/2e/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/2/2e/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ba3.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<dl><dd><em>Also known as: 把字句 ("bǎ"zìjù), 把 construction, preposition 把, disposal construction&#160;and pre-transitive 把.</em></dd></dl>
<p>The 把 (bǎ) sentence is a useful structure for constructing longer sentences which focus on the result or influence of an action. One of its key features is that it brings the object of the verb closer to the front of the sentence and precedes it with a 把. It's really common in Mandarin but can feel a bit awkward at first for English speakers.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#What_is_a_.E6.8A.8A_sentence.3F"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">What is a 把 sentence?</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#Key_Things_to_Keep_in_Mind_When_Using_.E6.8A.8A"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Key Things to Keep in Mind When Using 把</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#.E6.8A.8A_Sentences_with_Two_Objects"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">把 Sentences with Two Objects</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#.E6.8A.8A_Sentences_with_Complements"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">把 Sentences with Complements</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#Forming_.E6.8A.8A_Sentences"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Forming 把 Sentences</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-6"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#Negating_.E6.8A.8A_Sentences"><span class="tocnumber">5.1</span> <span class="toctext">Negating 把 Sentences</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-7"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#Question_Forms_of_.E6.8A.8A_Sentences"><span class="tocnumber">5.2</span> <span class="toctext">Question Forms of 把 Sentences</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-8"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#Adverbs_in_.E6.8A.8A_Sentences"><span class="tocnumber">5.3</span> <span class="toctext">Adverbs in 把 Sentences</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-9"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#.E6.8A.8A_Sentences_and_Quantity_Phrases"><span class="tocnumber">5.4</span> <span class="toctext">把 Sentences and Quantity Phrases</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-10"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#QUIZ_TIME.21"><span class="tocnumber">6</span> <span class="toctext">QUIZ TIME!</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#Ready_to_Check_Your_Mastery_of_.E6.8A.8A.3F"><span class="tocnumber">6.1</span> <span class="toctext">Ready to Check Your Mastery of 把?</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-11"><a href="Using_&quot;ba&quot;_sentences#Verbs_for_.E6.8A.8A_Sentences"><span class="tocnumber">7</span> <span class="toctext">Verbs for 把 Sentences</span></a></li>
